Christian J. Frank https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Christian_J._Frank 0 Christian J. Frank (13 March 1890 – 10 December 1967), was an American actor. He appeared in 65 films between 1920 and 1948, mostly in uncredited roles. His most notable role was that of an irascible cop in the Laurel and Hardy short You're Darn Tootin' (1928). He was born in New York, New York, United States and died in Los Angeles, California. Christian_J._Frank ( 13_March_1890 – 10_December_1967 ) , was an_American_actor .
